"{\"uid\": \"si.com-fannation-sneakers-news-rory-mcilroy-wears-ostrich-print-nike-golf-shoes-in-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Sunday marks the fourth and final round of the men's golf tournament at the 2024 Summer Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 100, \"end\": 105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999959518391, \"rank\": 4.048378639136344e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the more exciting storylines to follow has been the strong play of Rory McIlroy - and his fire footwear.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 181, \"end\": 193, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rory McIlroy\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13156709\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rory_McIlroy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 35-year-old is well-positioned to take home another Olympic medal, depending on how today plays out.\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy's play has been electrifying, which is perfectly fitting given his new golf shoes.\", \"from\": 325, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the tournament at Le Golf National, McIlroy has worn the newly-released Nike Victory Tour 3 Electric golf shoes.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 540, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 500, \"end\": 504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9633465449409746, \"rank\": 0.03804802578774847, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}, {\"begin\": 505, \"end\": 517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victory_Tour_(The_Jacksons_tour)\", \"score\": 0.9899381019339097, \"rank\": 0.010159316555065119, \"text\": \"Victory Tour\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victory_Tour_(The_Jacksons_tour)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victory_Tour_(The_Jacksons_tour)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The limited-edition colorway is part ofNike's 55-shoe 'Electric' packreleased for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 541, \"to\": 636, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes and fans can still buy the shoes in select sizes for $210 on theNike website.\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, other colorways of the model are still available in more sizes.\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 802, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike other styles, the 'Electric' colorway sports a white upper, black Swoosh logos, and a mix of Ostrich print and Solar Orange around the base of the shoes.\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 964, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 877, \"end\": 883, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swoosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Swoosh\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swoosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Swoosh\"}, {\"begin\": 904, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ostrich\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2555073097489202e-14, \"text\": \"Ostrich\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ostrich\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ostrich\"}, {\"begin\": 928, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"score\": 0.9999999998708518, \"rank\": 1.2895778205689546e-10, \"text\": \"Orange\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Orange_S.A.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Nike Victory Tour 3 is an elegant blend of style and performance.\", \"from\": 966, \"to\": 1035, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It features a full-grain leather upper with an internal strap for added support.\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An Air Zoom unit is stitched directly to the upper instead of being set into foam, so it responds to every step.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1230, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1125, \"end\": 1129, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoom_Video_Communications\", \"score\": 0.9001486288624387, \"rank\": 0.11082435678941956, \"text\": \"Zoom\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoom_Video_Communications\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoom_Video_Communications\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The full-length plate beneath the Air unit helps increase energy return.\", \"from\": 1231, \"to\": 1303, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lastly, the cushy foam under the heel delivers an extremely smooth ride.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Tour Flex Pro from Softspikes in the key three forefoot spike locations and Silver Tornado spikes in the lateral and heel offer exceptional traction in all conditions.\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1549, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Golfers who want to stand out while performing at the highest level cannot go wrong with the Nike Victory Tour 3 Electric.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If McIlroy can pull off a win on Sunday, then these shoes will become even more sought after by athletes.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 1779, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fans can follow\\u00c2Kicks on SI\\u00c2\\u00a0for all their sneaker news from golf and the rest of the sports world.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1880, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Further Reading:Adidas unveils its chaotic new spike-less golf shoes.\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Loading recommendations...\", \"from